@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Selected Day Prediction

actor Inspector
participant "Web Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Scenario Engine" as Scenario
participant "Feature Engine" as Features
participant "Scoring Service" as Scoring
database "PostGIS" as PostGIS
database "Analytics Store" as Analytics

Inspector -> Dashboard : choose farm and target day
Dashboard -> API : request prediction for selected day
API -> Scenario : build scenario context
Scenario -> PostGIS : load farm boundary and history
Scenario -> Analytics : load prior weather and satellite features
Scenario -> Features : request NDVI and soil wetness for day
Features -> Scenario : return field features
Scenario -> Scoring : calculate need, waste, and risk bands
Scoring -> Scenario : return predicted bands and explanation
Scenario -> API : response with selected-day prediction
API -> Dashboard : render risk color and evidence panel

@enduml